description.en: Kawai Shiba is a decentralized token, it works as an independent liquidity generation protocol and frictionless autonomous yield farming. With the innovative Kawai Shiba project, a constant market volume will be guaranteed so that holders can receive their passive BUSD earnings without doing anything.
